2.77 acre 280 sq.m. (4 plots). A popular tourist destination with 7 buildings total.  Main building is on top of hill with Thai-style wooden construction (teak wood, Makha wood) with 2 stunning pools in front and back.  The other 6 buildings are traditional clay construction guest homes.

The land is on top of a hill; the main house is on the highest point of the hill. This plot of land is 750 meters above sea level, cool throughout the year. There is an access road to the land, an asphalt road and a concrete road. There is a parking lot for about 20 cars. The surface is paved. There are 2 stunning pools in the front and the back. Is an unrivaled pool all year round. There are many perennial trees (Teak, Makha, Kanekra, Bamboo and Mango trees with fruits in the area of 28 acres). There are greenhouses, vegetables, tomatoes, Japanese melon, non-toxic with smart farm system. The resort consists of 8 bathrooms (1 unit). 2 workers' houses, 1 storage shed.

We are currently operating a farm stay: Grow vegetables in accordance with organic agriculture, fish farming, organic chicken farm, organic cafe and resort. The occupancy rate is almost 100% over the 4 months of the high seasons. 

Highlight:

Every plot has proper title deed. It is an area similar to a small mountain, with views around the village, rice fields, wind turbines and pine forests. There is a road leading to the public utility. High power systems enter the groundwater area of 80 meters deep and there is also a village water supply. Quiet, concrete road coming to the farm entrance.
